def_cn: （树）多节瘤的，扭曲的，疙疙瘩瘩的
def_en: A gnarled tree is twisted and strangely shaped because it is old.

def_cn: 长满皱纹的；皮肤粗糙的；关节扭曲的
def_en: A person who is gnarled looks very old because their skin has lines on it or their body is bent. If someone has gnarled hands, their hands are twisted as a result of old age or illness.
